ather unusual when participating in the most important sporting event on earth.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9936934989617662, \"rank\": 0.00567670695069876, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}, {\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999690685404, \"rank\": 2.1254922933365876e-08, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"Alain JOCARD\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"/ AFP\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"ALAIN JOCARD/AFP\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"The hand\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"the pocket pose\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"his totally relaxed state\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important sporting event\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a plain white Adidas T-shirt with Turkey across it, his attire was a far cry from the very stylishKim Yejiwho was playing a whole different game.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.324001730659604e-18, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi